Package: brackets
Title: Display Tournament Brackets
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Veerle", "Eeftink - van Leemput", , "veerle@hypebright.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Veerle van Leemput <veerle@hypebright.nl>
Description: Display HTML tournament brackets (round-robin, single
    elimination, double elimination) of any length at any stage of its
    lifetime. The data needed follows the opinionated brackets-model data
    structure.
